==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: By candle-light at the third watch, up with the chickens at the fifth watch.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: sān gēng dēng hŭo wŭ gēng jī

===Phrase===
'''[[三更]][[灯火]][[五更]][[鸡]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'')To [[burn the midnight oil]], only to get up at the crack of dawn.
# (''idiom'') To work long hours.

===Alternate forms===
[[三更]][[燈火]][[五更]][[雞]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

